  "description": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"4u0fp\",\"text\":\"Tris buffered saline (TBS) is a commonly used buffer with a wide range of applications in biochemistry. It is often more convenient to prepare a 10X solution so that additional components can be added when preparing the buffer on demand.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":[]}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
